comments: Towns (MIN) gathers the pass in the post and holds his position as Edwards (MIN) and the the trailing Osman (CLE) run around him. The contact with Osman is marginal.
Lopez (CLE) contest Edwards' (MIN) shot attempt at the rim and makes marginal contact with him.
Lopez (CLE) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as McDaniels attempts to get around the pick.

Gobert (MIN) moves alongside Garland's (CLE) path and absorbs the marginal contact by collapsing his forearm as the distance closes and then removing the marginal contact during the release of the driving shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Osman's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) reaches in for the ball and deflects Russell's (MIN) dribble, which Russell is able to swiftly recover.
Russell (MIN) takes less than 8 seconds to establish the ball in the frontcourt.
Stevens (CLE) moves into Russell's (MIN) space and marginal contact occurs with his side during his dribble in the frontcourt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Russell (MIN) loses control of the ball as he attempts to gather it. He is the last to touch the ball prior to it going out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to Cleveland.
McDaniels (MIN) moves laterally into Garland's (CLE) path and body contact occurs that affects Garland's SQBR during the pick.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Towns (MIN) and Stevens (CLE) engage and disengage away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Okoro's (CLE) path and incidental contact occurs as the players come together during the pick.
Lopez (CLE) legally contests Gobert's (MIN) elbow floater attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Lopez (CLE) establishes himself in Russell's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players engage as they move towards the basket.
Towns (MIN) legally contests Garland's (CLE) floater attempt in the paint.
Osman (CLE) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) brings his right hand completely underneath the ball during his dribble up the floor.
Garland's (CLE) off-hand lightly brushes Prince's (MIN) side and the contact at the end of the drive is marginal.
Osman (CLE) reaches in for the ball and Edwards (MIN) spins away from the marginal contact.
Stevens (CLE) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Osman (CLE) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) gets to ball height and dislodges the ball away from Stevens (CLE) during the rebounding opportunity.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Prince (MIN).
Garland (CLE) inbounds the ball within five seconds of having received it from the official.
Rivers (MIN) briefly holds his right hand to Garland's (CLE) front and he slides the marginal contact off as the players disengage over the screen.
Garland's (CLE) right heel comes down out of bounds after receiving the ball.
Anderson (MIN) legally contests Garland's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) initiates contact to Garland's (CLE) side that affects his control of the ball. The illegal contact occurs prior to Garland's upward shooting motion.
Okoro (CLE) extends his right arm out and steps towards Prince's (MIN) path when marginal contact occurs.
Towns (MIN) and Mobley (CLE) engage and disengage during the inbounds play.
Garland (CLE) commits a take foul on Russell (MIN).
Gobert (MIN) reaches around Mobley (CLE) and deflects the inbounds pass. The contact prior to the deflection is marginal.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Prince (MIN). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Anderson (MIN) legally contests Garland's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
